description:
Jinny`s Milotic (Feeby) is the evolved form of Jinny`s Feebas (Feeby). Meowth attempted to steal Feeby but it started to evolve. It protected Jinny and fought off Team Rocket`s Carvanha.
It probably also knows the moves Twister and Water Gun as moves that look like them were seen during the battle with Team Rocket but they were not officially identified.
name: Milokaross (Nami)
